---
<section class="px-container-padding mb-section-gap" id="services">
  <div class="mb-16" data-animate>
    <span class="font-label-mono text-label-mono text-primary uppercase mb-4 block">Capacidades Centrales</span>
    <h2 class="font-headline-xl text-headline-xl text-white">Soluciones Industriales</h2>
  </div>
  <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8" data-animate="stagger">
    <div class="p-4 border border-white/5 bg-surface-container-low">
      <div class="aspect-[4/3] mb-6 relative overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-high">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1509391366360-2e959784a276?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop'); filter: grayscale(30%);"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 w-10 h-10 bg-primary-container/30 border border-primary/40 flex items-center justify-center text-primary backdrop-blur-sm">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">grid_view</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-headline-lg text-[20px] md:text-[24px] text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">SISTEMAS FOTOVOLTAICOS INDUSTRIALES</h3>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-body-md">
        Ingeniería e instalación de arreglos solares sobre techos industriales, naves y estacionamientos (carports) utilizando paneles bifaciales Tier 1 para un rendimiento óptimo.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4 border border-white/5 bg-surface-container-low">
      <div class="aspect-[4/3] mb-6 relative overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-high">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop'); filter: grayscale(30%);"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 w-10 h-10 bg-secondary-container/30 border border-secondary/40 flex items-center justify-center text-secondary backdrop-blur-sm" style="box-shadow: 0 0 15px rgba(255, 159, 0, 0.2);">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">battery_0_bar</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-headline-lg text-[20px] md:text-[24px] text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">ALMACENAMIENTO DE ENERGÍA (BESS)</h3>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-body-md">
        Sistemas de baterías de litio de alta capacidad para gestionar el consumo en horas pico y garantizar la continuidad operativa ante fallas de la red eléctrica.
      </p>
    </div>
    <div class="p-4 border border-white/5 bg-surface-container-low">
      <div class="aspect-[4/3] mb-6 relative overflow-hidden bg-surface-container-high">
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-cover bg-center" style="background-image: url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1551288049-bebda4e38f71?q=80&w=1200&auto=format&fit=crop'); filter: grayscale(30%);"></div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 to-transparent"></div>
        <div class="absolute bottom-3 left-3 w-10 h-10 bg-tertiary-container/30 border border-tertiary/40 flex items-center justify-center text-tertiary backdrop-blur-sm">
          <span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">show_chart</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <h3 class="font-headline-lg text-[20px] md:text-[24px] text-white mb-4 uppercase tracking-wide">AUDITORÍA Y EFICIENCIA ENERGÉTICA</h3>
      <p class="text-on-surface-variant leading-relaxed text-body-md">
        Despliegue de sensores IoT y software en la nube para auditar fugas de energía, medir el factor de potencia y optimizar el consumo de maquinaria pesada.
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
